*Između* njih dvoje postoji velika ljubav. (Between them there is great love.) 

Ona je živela *između* dva grada. (She lived between two cities.)

Moj brat i ja smo se igrali *između* namestaja. (My brother and I were playing between the furniture.)

On je dugo čekao *između* šetnje i obroka. (He waited for a long time between the walk and the meal.)

*Između* dva susreta su prošla tri godine. (Three years passed between two meetings.)